## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **zuranolone Zurzuvae 2023** = first FDA oral PPD (15-day 14-day course). brexanolone IV 60시간 REMS limitation 의 oral alternative. GABAA δ-subunit positive allosteric modulator (neurosteroid). quantum-VQE 의 allosteric pocket leverage.
2. **fezolinetant Veozah 2023** = first FDA NK3R antagonist 폐경 vasomotor (HFI hot flash). HRT estrogens 의 non-hormonal alternative — WHI 2002 post-era women's choice. quantum-VQE 의 GPCR pocket fit.
3. **brexanolone Zulresso 2019** = first FDA IV PPD (60시간 IV, REMS-only). PPD pharmacology paradigm shift — antidepressant 가 아닌 GABAA neurosteroid 가 first-line specific drug. zuranolone 도입 후 IV 사용 제한적.
4. **relugolix-E2-NET Myfembree 2021** = first GnRH antag combo 자궁근종 + 자궁내막증. add-back E2+NET 가 hot flash + 골밀도 보호. quantum-VQE 의 GPCR antagonist + combination formulation cross.
5. **TXA WOMAN trial 2017** = 산후 출혈 mortality 감소 demonstration. WHO 권장 표준. plasmin inhibitor — 응급 임상 약물 (cross-emergency_medicine).
6. **carbetocin heat-stable 2010+ EU/CA** = oxytocin Pitocin 의 heat-stable analog — low-resource setting + cold-chain 부재 환경에서 산후 자궁수축. oxytocin-R selectivity 동일 + heat stability formulation engineering.
7. **aspirin 81mg 자간전증 1차예방 USPSTF 2021** = high-risk 12주부터 — 임상 표준 변화. low-dose 가 disease-modifying.
8. **mifepristone + misoprostol telehealth 2021+** = 임신중지 가정 self-managed paradigm shift (post-Dobbs 2022 US 일부 주 제한). pharmacology + access policy cross.
9. **HPV9 27-45 expansion 2018 + 임신 코로나 mRNA + Tdap + flu** = preventive + vaccinology cross-link 표준. ACIP recommendations 임상 적용.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, 임신/모유 수유 환자 RCT exclusion 표준 → real-world evidence 의존.

